race.comment: STELLAR MOFEED (4) looks well placed second up. She was off a 10 month spell at Sandown Lakeside but ran much better than her $20 SP would've suggested, sticking on gamely for second in a tougher race. She should strip fitter now and get every chance from the inside gate. GRACIOUS DIVA (9) is knocking on the door having just found one better in her past two starts, getting too far back on each occasion. She draws wide again but will be hard to hold out with the right run. LULU DARLING (2) has placed in both runs back and should be at peak fitness with strong winning claims. ZADAR SUNSET (3) was okay fresh and can sneak into the money.
